      <title>乐天考虑合并金融部门；股价跳涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/rakuten-considers-combining-financial-units-shares-jump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负债累累的在线零售商乐天集团表示，将考虑合并其金融部门以促进合作。]]></description>
