    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安在土耳其市政选举中惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/erdogan-suffers-defeat-in-turkey-s-municipal-elections-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 在投票箱中对主要反对党遭遇了前所未有的失败，原因是通货膨胀猖獗，借贷成本达到二十多年前总统上台以来的最高水平。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/erdogan-suffers-defeat-in-turkey-s-municipal-elections-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 04:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国房屋销售持续低迷，几乎没有任何好转的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/china-home-sales-drought-persists-with-little-recovery-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份中国房屋销售持续低迷。根据中国房地产信息集团的初步数据，继 2 月份下降 60% 后，100 家最大房地产公司的新房销售价值同比下降约 46% 至 3580 亿元人民币（496 亿美元）。资料来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/china-home-sales-drought-persists-with-little-recovery-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:36:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国人涌入印度债券引起市场轰动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/foreigners-flocking-to-indian-bonds-make-a-splash-across-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度被纳入主要全球债券指数的分水岭，大量资金涌入印度，正在重塑这个长期渴望免受热钱流入影响的国家的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/foreigners-flocking-to-indian-bonds-make-a-splash-across-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国建筑业前景黯淡，铁矿石跌至 10 个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iron-ore-sinks-to-10-month-low-on-gloom-over-china-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于炼钢材料面临中国建筑活动疲软和供应再度激增的双重打击，铁矿石价格跌至 10 个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iron-ore-sinks-to-10-month-low-on-gloom-over-china-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管销售放缓，新加坡房价再次上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/singapore-home-prices-rise-for-third-quarter-defying-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管销售量持续数月不温不火，且当局发出高利率警告，但新加坡房价连续第三个季度上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/singapore-home-prices-rise-for-third-quarter-defying-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 00:58:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受青睐的美联储通胀指标推动金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/gold-xauusd-hits-record-on-fed-cut-outlook-and-geopolitical-tension</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于有迹象表明美联储即将降息，金价上涨至创纪录水平，这为金价上涨提供了动力，而金价上涨也是由地缘政治紧张局势和强劲的中国需求推动的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/gold-xauusd-hits-record-on-fed-cut-outlook-and-geopolitical-tension</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 00:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国需求成为焦点，石油价格在季度稳步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在第一季度强劲上涨后小幅走高，因中国复苏的迹象提振了需求前景。]]></description>
